       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. V3-LEN.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 I PIC 9(9) COMP.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 A.
       02 A-VALS COMP-1 OCCURS 3 TIMES.
       01 R COMP-1.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING A,R.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
       MOVE 0.0 TO R
       PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > 3
         COMPUTE R = R + (A-VALS(I) * A-VALS(I))
       END-PERFORM.
         COMPUTE R = FUNCTION SQRT(R).

       END PROGRAM V3-LEN.

       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. V3-NORM.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 I PIC 9(9) COMP.
