       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 A.
       02 A-VALS COMP-1 OCCURS 3 TIMES.
       01 R.
       02 R-VALS COMP-1 OCCURS 3 TIMES.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING A,R.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.

       CALL 'V3-LEN' USING A, LEN
       PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > 3
         COMPUTE R-VALS(I) = A-VALS(I) / LEN
       END-PERFORM.

       END PROGRAM V3-NORM.
